{"tid":1289491,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"笑話一則（純發夢）","createTime":"2019-07-06T06:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T06:22:09.000Z","uid":172376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"672d297ee5e8926537b30f5eca0e3140e5a17f00","tid":1289491,"uid":172376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:18:38.000Z","msg":"話說我上個禮拜發夢<br />\n去左同一班auntie uncle食飯<br />\n咁講到話班年輕人衝擊立法會<br />\n政府又話要2億整番好乜乜柒柒啦<br />\n跟住有個廢中講左句<br />\n「我每年交十幾萬稅架啵即係用我啲錢去整呀，點解唔叫班後生仔俾番，話知佢地賠到破產...」<br />\n突然坐我左邊嘅uncle講左句<br />\n「一年交十幾萬稅咁少就咪撚講野啦，我都未出聲」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係笑左出嚟<br />\n點解啲廢中有小小錢就吵77<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">我無野講</code></pre>"},{"pid":"17e79428fdb378120f67c7dd7796a2f625627ef0","tid":1289491,"uid":172376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"真心一年交十幾萬稅好多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}